  "text": "Genetic context of bla GES-6 . In order to assess whether the bla GES-6 gene was indeed located on the chromosome of P. aeruginosa BOR as reported for the GES-6-producing ST235 isolate FFUP_PS_690 [CITATION_1] , PCR mapping was performed with a series of primers designed inside and outside the ICE reported in that genome (see Table S1 in the supplemental material).",
